history.content:
One way to know is by ordering a transcript for $1.90 on Calcentral

(go to Calcentral My Academics --> Academic Records --> Transcript - Undergraduate or Graduate Students --> Order Electronic/PDF Transcript)

===========================================================

If you are on campus, you can also go to 120 Sproul Hall and get a hardcopy of your transcript for free, which will show your honors to date. 

----------
